revision.text:
{{documentation subpage}}

Given a decimal coordinate, two cardinal directions, and precision, render a coordinate in degrees/minutes/seconds.

=== Usage ===
 &#123;{coord/dec2dms|''coord''|N|S|''precision''}}
 &#123;{coord/dec2dms|''coord''|E|W|''precision''}}

Precision codes:
{| class="wikitable"
| d || Degrees (rounded to integer)
|-
| d1 || Degrees (rounded to 0.1 degrees)
|-
| dm || Degrees, minutes (rounded to integer)
|-
| dm1 || Degrees, minutes (rounded to 0.1 minutes)
|-
| dms || Degrees, minutes, seconds (rounded to integer)
|-
| dms1 || Degrees, minutes, seconds (rounded to 0.1 seconds)
|}

=== Examples ===
{| class="wikitable"
|-
| <code><nowiki>{{Coord/dec2dms|10.391944|N|S|d}}</nowiki></code>    || {{Coord/dec2dms|10.391944|N|S|d}}
|-
| <code><nowiki>{{Coord/dec2dms|10.391944|N|S|d1}}</nowiki></code>   || {{Coord/dec2dms|10.391944|N|S|d1}}
|-
| <code><nowiki>{{Coord/dec2dms|10.390000|N|S|d}}</nowiki></code>    || {{Coord/dec2dms|10.390000|N|S|d}}
|-
| <code><nowiki>{{Coord/dec2dms|10.390000|N|S|d1}}</nowiki></code>   || {{Coord/dec2dms|10.390000|N|S|d1}}
|-
| <code><nowiki>{{Coord/dec2dms|10.39|N|S|d}}</nowiki></code>        || {{Coord/dec2dms|10.39|N|S|d}}
|-
| <code><nowiki>{{Coord/dec2dms|10.39|N|S|d1}}</nowiki></code>       || {{Coord/dec2dms|10.39|N|S|d1}}
|-
| <code><nowiki>{{Coord/dec2dms|-10.391944|N|S|dm}}</nowiki></code>  || {{Coord/dec2dms|-10.391944|N|S|dm}}
|-
| <code><nowiki>{{Coord/dec2dms|-10.391944|N|S|dm1}}</nowiki></code> || {{Coord/dec2dms|-10.391944|N|S|dm1}}
|-
| <code><nowiki>{{Coord/dec2dms|10.391944|E|W|dms}}</nowiki></code>  || {{Coord/dec2dms|10.391944|E|W|dms}}
|-
| <code><nowiki>{{Coord/dec2dms|10.391944|E|W|dms1}}</nowiki></code> || {{Coord/dec2dms|10.391944|E|W|dms1}}
|-
| <code><nowiki>{{Coord/dec2dms|10|N|S|d}}</nowiki></code>           || {{Coord/dec2dms|10|N|S|d}}
|-
| <code><nowiki>{{Coord/dec2dms|10|E|W|dm}}</nowiki></code>          || {{Coord/dec2dms|10|E|W|dm}}
|-
| <code><nowiki>{{Coord/dec2dms|-10|E|W|dms}}</nowiki></code>        || {{Coord/dec2dms|-10|E|W|dms}}
|-
| <code><nowiki>{{Coord/dec2dms|-10|E|W|dms1}}</nowiki></code>       || {{Coord/dec2dms|-10|E|W|dms1}}
|-
|}

