{{Documentation subpage}}
"'''<u>N</u>'''umber '''<u>T</u>'''able '''<u>S</u>'''orting, '''<u>C</u>'''onverted". Use this to sort converted units in tables with one template.

=== Usage ===
Example:
{| style="background:transparent; width:100%;" 
| <pre>
{| class="wikitable sortable" 
! City !! Elevation
|-
| Budapest || {{ntsc|606|ft}}
|-
| Denver || {{ntsc|5280|ft}}
|-
| Fairbanks || {{ntsc|446|ft}}
|-
| Glasgow || {{ntsc|351|ft}}
|-
| Mexico City || {{ntsc|7349|ft}}
|-
| New Orleans || {{ntsc|-6|ft}}
|}</pre> || style="width:1em;" | ||
